data.description: This very spacious, well-appointed home sitting on a large corner lot with a huge private pool surrounded by woods is ready for new owners! The coveted Elkins Lake community offers so much from the lake, recreation and the golf course! With an updated traditional style, a whole home generator, his & hers primary closets and oversized 3 car garage, this home has all of the amenities and space that you could want. Newer roof (2018), new spa heater (March 2023), new pool filter (July 2023). Schedule your tour today.
